How to create a catchy hook to 10X your views👇

It’s all about those first 3-5 seconds of your video.

People’s attention spans are like that of a goldfish.

You have to grab your viewers’ attention right from the beginning.

If you do, you’ll get a lot of views.

I’d recommend 3 strategies:
Bold statement: Here’s how you ___ ((specific desired outcome) Question: How to ____ (specific desired outcome)? Intrigue: Never do this if you want ____ (specific desired outcome)
 TOP-10 ideas for your hooks: The secret to ____ (I.e. gain followers)
You need to stop ____ (I.e. delete your reels)
The biggest mistake all ___ (I.e. realtors) make
This is a reminder to ___ (I.e. stay fit)
Here’s the shortcut to ___ (i.e. get clients on Insta)
How to ___ (I.e. avoid burn out)
Why is nobody talking about ___ (I.e. self love)
This is going to be controversial, but ___ 
BREAKING NEWS!

caption.text:
Photo content is back🔥

According to my Instagram Insights My carousels got 680,000 views in the last 30 days.

And sometimes they generate me even more leads and engagement than reels!

Here are a few tips to get more views with carousels:

👉The more slides the better

👉 UPDATE: Each carousel post can now have up to 20 photos or videos instead of 10!!!
